resources.string:
"
        Please generate a concise summary for the following recurrence rule, with a clear expression of the frequency and conditions of the recurrence, and use natural, concise language.

        Requirements:

        - Consider all relevant details of the recurrence rule, including frequency, period, end conditions, etc., to ensure the summary is comprehensive and accurate;
        - Output the summary text only; explanatory prefixes such as "Summary:" or "My suggestion is" are prohibited;
        - Markdown formatting and unnecessary punctuation are prohibited;
        - Line breaks are prohibited.

        The following is a recurrence rule that conforms to the iCalendar RRULE specification.

        %s
    "
